From the manufacturer

Samsonite Centric 2 Hardside Dual-Spinner 2-Piece Set

Set includes one carry-on (meets most domestic carry-on size requirements) and one medium spinner (ideal checked bag for longer trips).

Plenty of room to keep all your clothes crease-free and safely in place

Two Piece Luggage Set

Centric 2 combines scratch-resistant textures with lightweight 100% polycarbonate construction, ensuring your luggage looks as great on the 100th trip as it does on the first.

This lightweight line offers heavyweight protection riding on effortless 360 Spinner Wheels. Dont pull your case; let Centric roll comfortably beside you on your journey.

  • TSA lock (medium spinner)
  • Lightweight 100% polycarbonate
  • 360 spinner wheels
  • Carry-On (wheels to top): 21.5" x 14" x 9", 6.6 lbs
  • Medium (wheels to top): 28" x 18.5" x 11.8", 8.8 lbs

USB charger

Enjoy the luxury of a charging system that travels with you, designed to connect with your preferred battery (carry-on only)

Spinner wheels

Four, multi- directional oversized spinner wheels for effortless mobility

Expandable

Design includes expansion for added capacity when needed

Polycarbonate

Scratch-resistant polycarbonate brushed-textured shell reflects light and protects from scratches, keeping cases beautiful trip after trip

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.
